name: Complete the registration, login, purchase, and order confirmation process

testSteps.description: 1: Complete the registration, login, purchase, and order confirmation process ({firstName=Jane, lastName=Smith, email=jane.smith33@example.com, telephone=987654321, password=password456, confirmPassword=password456, newPassword=password12345, producto=MacBook Pro, secondProducto=Samsung Galaxy})

children.description: Given I fill in the registration form with first name "Jane", last name "Smith", email "jane.smith33@example.com", telephone "987654321", password "password456", confirm password "password456" and save the register
When The user validates the login
And The user resets the password "password12345"
And The user navigates to the Laptops & Notebooks section and selects the Show all laptops & notebooks option
Mariana clicks on Show All Laptops & Notebooks
And The user adds a "MacBook Pro" to the shopping cart
And The user uses the search bar to find a "Samsung Galaxy" and adds it to the cart
And The user removes "MacBook Pro" from the cart
And The user adds another unit of "Samsung Galaxy" to the cart
And The user completes the purchase process up to the order confirmation
Mariana clicks on term and conditions
Then The user should see the order confirmation
